Attentively listening to the last will of the late Emperor

7
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:04,300
and solemnly bearing the weight of succession,

8
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,400
His Royal Highness respectfully follows the imperial decree,

9
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:11,720
and informs the world,
on the twenty-fourth day of the second month,

10
00:01:11,870 --> 00:01:14,870
that he's to ascend to the throne as Emperor.

11
00:01:17,270 --> 00:01:18,510
My dear Big Brother.

12
00:01:22,330 --> 00:01:23,330
