66
00:04:20,269 --> 00:04:21,800
Do you still want to deny it?

67
00:04:23,150 --> 00:04:23,950
Impossible.

68
00:04:24,450 --> 00:04:28,530
Ever since you failed to capture the remnants of the previous dynasty's death warriors,

69
00:04:28,530 --> 00:04:31,260
I've been hoping that one day you would turn back.

70
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:36,020
Should we recall the guards who are investigating
the remnants of the death warriors?

71
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:36,630
No need.

72
00:04:40,470 --> 00:04:42,270
We must not miss any clue.

73
00:04:42,590 --> 00:04:44,830
