83
00:05:08,990 --> 00:05:09,790
You thought

84
00:05:10,850 --> 00:05:14,320
you could rest easy after allying with the four monarchs?

85
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,490
Unfortunately,

86
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:20,300
